A video which has gone viral on social media showing the moment a woman showed love to her husband on his birthday. The unnamed woman could be seen spraying the money alleged to be about N500,000 on her husband. In the video, the woman stepped into the room while her husband was sleeping and started N1000 notes on him without him noticing. Her accomplice could be heard reigning praises on her as she sprays the money, shouting that the next year would be in dollars. At the beginning of the video, she shows the bundles of N1000 notes she was about to spray on her husband. Her husband wakes up wearing matching sleeping wear with his wife, smiling happily as he hugs her for the birthday love. Watch video below: